  "PublicRemarks": "Welcome to this bright and spacious 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom townhouse condo with vaulted ceilings in the living room and kitchen. The kitchen features granite countertops, pantry, quiet-close cabinetry, and a full appliance package including a fridge and dishwasher replaced in 2025. The primary bedroom includes a 4-piece ensuite, while the second bedroom and full bath offer great flexibility. In-suite laundry with stacked washer and dryer (new in 2025). Enjoy a south-facing balcony off the living room. Two portable air conditioning units are included for added comfort. Comes with two outdoor parking stalls — one titled and one assigned. (31751317)",
